{"tid":984790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"火警毀電錶房　太和邨斷水電40小時","createTime":"2019-01-17T05:34:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T16:42:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"16782a58b3085d205555dd02b121dbd97e8d718a","tid":984790,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T05:34:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190117/20592860\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190117%2F20592860&d=UvKuUuc4QvHjzgPyDvtmWy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=313b346f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190117%2F20592860&h=2d6d217d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190117/20592860</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月17日 <br />\n<br />\n火警毀電錶房　太和邨斷水電40小時<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190117/large/17la7p02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190117%2Flarge%2F17la7p02.jpg&h=bd04519a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n互委會提供臨時充電站，讓街坊為手機充電。劉柏麟攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】大埔太和邨喜和樓電錶房日前發生火警，居民斷水斷電近40小時，至昨日凌晨始恢復食水供應，升降機有限度服務，居於高層的長者無奈留守家中。大廈法團指，由於電錶房內不少配件停產，承辦商未能即時找到合適替換，導致一直未能恢復供電。<br />\n<br />\n太和邨喜和樓地下電錶房，周一下午3時發生火警，電線盡毀，導致全幢住戶單位無電，連帶升降機、食水泵、鹹水泵亦無法運作，住戶斷水斷電。至昨凌晨4時，公眾照明系統及食水恢復供應，兩部升降機重投運作，但單位未恢復供電。<br />\n<br />\n居於23樓的長者蘇太指，停電當日剛巧外出，事後無法回家，「等個仔收工，慢慢扶我上嚟，一路行一路氣喘」。同層手持枴杖的伯伯稱，由於行動不便，停電兩天無落過樓，「出事嗰日我喺樓下行返上嚟，腳都震埋」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n義工行35層樓梯派飯<br />\n<br />\n他笑言停水兩天沒洗澡，幸好有人上門送飯送水。有居民投訴無廁所水，無法沖廁，「臭到冤，冚埋蓋都好臭」。住戶楊太則表示，火警當天被困升降機個多小時，停水兩天需到體育館洗澡，由於要接送孫兒上學，因此每天不停爬樓梯上落。<br />\n<br />\n法團主席任小姐指，太和邨樓齡逾30年，電錶房電線老化，大部份配件停產，承辦商未能一時三刻找到適合的電線及配件，故一直未能恢復供電。任稱太和邨有不少長者居民，無電無升降機造成極大不便，法團及管業處即時聯絡社署及招募義工上門派飯派水，前日就有50多名義工爬35層樓梯，到各戶派飯派水解燃眉之急。<br />\n<br />\n■記者劉柏麟  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n塱原建自然生態公園<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n社交網「大量張學友飛」引黃牛黨現身　內地男遭南亞賊搶14萬元"},{"pid":"b46dbcbe30144abf375801a848da060d1bf48890","tid":984790,"uid":85427,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T05:37:21.000Z","msg":"辛苦義工了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae46c6791b29b4ef9b90485b6fb653672bd58182","tid":984790,"uid":23947,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T05:47:01.000Z","msg":"公屋撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918119447d24041c90d819b4f2767a7b440a18ca","tid":984790,"uid":32661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae46c6791b29b4ef9b90485b6fb653672bd58182","tid":984790,"uid":23947,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T05:47:01.000Z","msg":"公屋撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T05:48:51.000Z","msg":"太和買左嫁啦<br />\n應該叫私人物業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3e8d04c2cb0cf10b8e01e5c2c86f4528ce2dbc","tid":984790,"uid":85427,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae46c6791b29b4ef9b90485b6fb653672bd58182","tid":984790,"uid":23947,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T05:47:01.000Z","msg":"公屋撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T05:50:39.000Z","msg":"買了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2010718c976186701042010eb4b3cd46c0a24742","tid":984790,"uid":46925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2